Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

## ── Secrets & local config (never commit) ─────────────────────
appsettings.*.local.json
secrets.json
.env
.env.*
*.pfx

# User Secrets live outside the repo; keep local overrides out
appsettings.Development.local.json

## ── IDE / AI assistants (local only) ──────────────────────────
